    89	- **No refresh path exists** `A1`: `podAnnotations: {}`; no `reloader.stakater.com/*` annotation; no config-checksum annotation; no Stakater Reloader controller in the cluster; readiness/liveness probes are `httpGet /healthz` only, so a pod serving a dead credential still reports **Ready**.
