183-| 3 Reproduce cold | Reproduction path | probe = question+authority | L11 table | Steps 1–7 | "just rerun the pipeline" | L11 |
184:| 4 Reject false explanations | Verification + on-call recognition | discriminator splits 401/403 | L4 + L12 | Step 2 | network / role / portal confusions | L4, L8, L10, L12 |
185-| 5 Repair safely | Fix mechanism + IaC | one-way doors; least privilege | how-to-fix tree | Steps 4–7 | "disable local auth / grant Data Owner" | L8, how-to-fix.md |
